text: Great place to relax and enjoy rugby!

name: Lee held
text: Great group of gracious people. Field is beautiful...

name: Michael Laney
text: Birmingham Rugby is very welcoming to fans as well as new players even if they don’t know the rules of the sport yet. They even have coed flag rugby for age 6-11 in addition to tackle rugby for u15, u19, and the adult team. The website has lots of up to date info.

name: Brendan Smith
text: One of the best decisions of my life was joining the Birmingham Vulcan’s Rugby Club. Not only do you learn how to play the best sport in the world but you get to develop friendships that will last a life time. Great club for both experienced players and players that are new to the sport.

name: Jakeb Glaser
text: Great family atmosphere! Very welcoming to new players no matter the age or experience. Spectating the games is always a fun social event even when you don’t know the sport because they’ll easily explain what’s going on.

name: Brett Walsh
text:
Joined up 3 weeks ago and haven't looked back since. Family-oriented style club with a good sense of humor and also great way to get in shape!

Edit: a year and a bit later I'm still at the club! We've grown immensely in my short time being a part of it and have so many 1st time rugby players joining up! Everyone is super encouraging and a team/family first mentality is very welcoming! No matter my attitude after a terrible day at work, i always leave the pitch after practice in good spirits! I'll add to my edit next year after I've completed my 2nd year with them!

name: Scott Petersen
text: The club has been extremely welcoming since I moved to Birmingham in June. The team has created a family friendly atmosphere and gladly welcome newcomers to the sport.

name: AJ Reece
text: Fantastic group of guys who will help teach the game of rugby to any new comers. It’s a team on the field and a brotherhood off.

name: Sara Truett
text: Going to Vulcans games is a blast. Rugby has been such a fun sport to learn and going to their games is great on a Saturday afternoon.

name: charles bradbary
text: Great group of guys who are more like a family then just a club. If you are looking for somthing to do on a saturday come out to a game. Or a sport to join I highly recconmand cheeking out this sport!!

name: Michael Adams
text: Cool field, great times, and competitive rugby! Can't ask for anything more.

name: Cory Truett
text: Great club with an exceptional group of people.
